11#include "rtc_base/proxy_info.h"
12
13namespace rtc {
14
15const char* ProxyToString(ProxyType proxy) {
16 const char* const PROXY_NAMES[] = {"none", "https", "socks5", "unknown"};
17 return PROXY_NAMES[proxy];
18}
19
20ProxyInfo::ProxyInfo() : type(PROXY_NONE), autodetect(false) {}
21ProxyInfo::~ProxyInfo() = default;
22
23} // namespace rtc
